metadata.name: Kong Punk #00001
metadata.description:
Kpunks is a 10,000 unit collection on the Ethereum blockchain.All Cyberkong Punks consist of a combination of over thousands of unique combinations with various rarities that give each punk a distinct reason to stay on top.
By taking the characteristically distinguished look and feel of CyberKong and combining them with the symbolic punks, the resulting output is truly spectacular. Uniquely generated, no two cyberkong punk are exactly alike, and their rarity scales from normal to extremely rare to legendary.
